The '''Roman Catholic Diocese of Malindi''' ({{lang-la|Malindien(sis)}}) is a [[diocese]] located in the city of [[Malindi]] in the [[Ecclesiastical province]] of [[Roman Catholic Archdiocese of Mombasa|Mombasa]] in [[Kenya]].
==History== * June 2, 2000: Established as Diocese of Malindi from the [[Diocese of Garissa]] and Metropolitan Archdiocese of Mombasa.<ref>{{Catholic-hierarchy|diocese|dmali|Diocese of Malindi|21 January 2015}}</ref>
